sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente (React)
    participant G as API Gateway (Nginx)
    participant D as Debt Service (C++)
    participant T as Transaction Service
    participant W as Wallet Service
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant KF as Kafka

    C->>G: POST /debts/{id}/payments (amount, date)
    G->>D: Proxy → /debts/{id}/payments
    
    Note over D: Autenticar usuario via Keycloak
    
    D->>P: SELECT * FROM debts WHERE id = $1
    P-->>D: debt (type, walletId, remainingBalance)
    
    D->>T: POST /transactions (crear transacción de pago)
    T-->>D: transactionId
    
    D->>W: PUT /wallets/{id} (actualizar balance)
    W-->>D: OK
    
    D->>P: INSERT INTO debt_payments (debt_id, amount, date)
    D->>P: UPDATE debts SET remaining_balance = $1
    
    D->>KF: Produce evento "payment_added" (topic: debt-events)
    
    D-->>C: 201 Created (paymentId, remainingBalance)